rm_dtt_intoxication :

rm for Random.

This map is based on de_dtt_intoxication : http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/186394 & cs_dtt_intoxication : http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/186395.

But this one include CS and DE game-mode. Indeed, each round will generate a new layout for the map and may switch the game-mode and the teams spawn-points.

For more information you can check the two other maps of this series or check out our E-M@il in the archive .txt file.
